title: Hawaii telescope protesters leave camp due to virus concerns
description: HONOLULU (AP) — Opponents of the Thirty Meter Telescope project on Hawaii island have pulled out of their camp due to concerns over the spread of the coronavirus.
content:
HONOLULU (AP) Opponents of the Thirty Meter Telescope project on Hawaii island have pulled out of their camp due to concerns over the spread of the coronavirus.
